descriptionHtml:
Useable Giants Club Plugin Release by MrGenki

____________________________
Welcome folks,this a just a small plugin that allows you to collect the giants club and use it yourself.The orginal club wasnt changed at all,it\'s just collect - and useable.Even enchantable.
The club is a 2H weapon.

____________________________
Installation:
Just put the extracted file into your DATA folder

____________________________
Note:
Not sure for in what version of the game it will run.
The orginal master file was edited.

____________________________
Credits:
Bethesda
